Message.SourceString: The wind smells briefly of grass and soil. A contented feeling fills your heart.
Message.LocalizedString: The wind smells briefly of grass and soil. A contented feeling fills your heart.

Message.SourceString: The well contains cold, stagnant water.
Message.LocalizedString: The well contains cold, stagnant water.

Message.SourceString: [You'll need to find some way to understand what they're saying.]
Message.LocalizedString: [You'll need to find some way to understand what they're saying.]

Message.SourceString: I tried to row out by the lake near the temple, when that dragon whacked me with his tail. What had I ever done to him?
Message.LocalizedString: I tried to row out by the lake near the temple, when that dragon whacked me with his tail. What had I ever done to him?

Message.SourceString: Names to be remembered. Prayers for the dead. Whisper our memories at the place by the temple, so that we might finally rest.
Message.LocalizedString: Names to be remembered. Prayers for the dead. Whisper our memories at the place by the temple, so that we might finally rest.

Message.SourceString: I'm impressed it got this far, really, this boat. Because I never sailed it here.
Message.LocalizedString: I'm impressed it got this far, really, this boat. Because I never sailed it here.

Message.SourceString: Then a great bloody dragon messed everything up.
Message.LocalizedString: Then a great bloody dragon messed everything up.

Message.SourceString: Dead within moments. Barely a day in this land. I never did have the best luck.
Message.LocalizedString: Dead within moments. Barely a day in this land. I never did have the best luck.

Message.SourceString: Remember me, adventurer. I was Lazina, blade for hire and swordmaster supreme. Say a prayer for me, so that the gods will look on me fondly.
Message.LocalizedString: Remember me, adventurer. I was Lazina, blade for hire and swordmaster supreme. Say a prayer for me, so that the gods will look on me fondly.

Message.SourceString: OoooOOooOOoooOOooo
Message.LocalizedString: OoooOOooOOoooOOooo

Message.SourceString: Remember me, adventurer. Say a farewell to Finn, won't you? Tell ma I'm sorry, and tell my stepda he's an arse.
Message.LocalizedString: Remember me, adventurer. Say a farewell to Finn, won't you? Tell ma I'm sorry, and tell my stepda he's an arse.

Message.SourceString: He knew of this place, that dragon. Poked his great scaley head through the entrance and grinned at me as he slowly drew in a breath. I watched my life unfold before me, until the poison put it all to an end. I wish I'd found that shield.
Message.LocalizedString: He knew of this place, that dragon. Poked his great scaley head through the entrance and grinned at me as he slowly drew in a breath. I watched my life unfold before me, until the poison put it all to an end. I wish I'd found that shield.

Message.SourceString: You see something glinting in the bucket. Reaching into the cold water, you pull out a strange looking amulet that's even colder to the touch.
Message.LocalizedString: You see something glinting in the bucket. Reaching into the cold water, you pull out a strange looking amulet that's even colder to the touch.

Message.SourceString: [You'll need to find some way to understand what they're saying.]
Message.LocalizedString: [You'll need to find some way to understand what they're saying.]

Message.SourceString: I wasn't. Shocker.
Message.LocalizedString: I wasn't. Shocker.

Message.SourceString: Once it was homes, standing together. Now, nothing but ruins, falling apart. The last surviving memories trampled beneath angry hooves. Find the name of the forgotten, set him free.
Message.LocalizedString: Once it was homes, standing together. Now, nothing but ruins, falling apart. The last surviving memories trampled beneath angry hooves. Find the name of the forgotten, set him free.

Message.SourceString: My brother lies buried in darkness, beneath a southern point rising high in the sky. Find his name, set him free.
Message.LocalizedString: My brother lies buried in darkness, beneath a southern point rising high in the sky. Find his name, set him free.

Message.SourceString: I came to rebuild a farmstead. Now I'll serve as nothing but compost. Gran would be so upset with me.
Message.LocalizedString: I came to rebuild a farmstead. Now I'll serve as nothing but compost. Gran would be so upset with me.

Message.SourceString: Choking on swamp gas. Ruined timber, mouldy and splintered. Sinking moment by moment into bitter, bleak, mud. Find the name of the buried, set them free.
Message.LocalizedString: Choking on swamp gas. Ruined timber, mouldy and splintered. Sinking moment by moment into bitter, bleak, mud. Find the name of the buried, set them free.

Message.SourceString: The dead do not yet feel fully at peace. There may be more out that need help moving on.

Message.LocalizedString: Blades that once whirled like a tornado, now lay still among crumbled stone. Find the lost who dwells there, set her free.

Message.SourceString: She was wrong, of course. They killed me. So I should hate them.
Message.LocalizedString: She was wrong, of course. They killed me. So I should hate them.

Message.SourceString: Remember me, adventurer. Help my spirit rest. Warren was my name, don't let it be forgotten.
Message.LocalizedString: Remember me, adventurer. Help my spirit rest. Warren was my name, don't let it be forgotten.

Message.SourceString: You hear the sound of laughter and the clash of blade against blade. You cannot help but smile.
Message.LocalizedString: You hear the sound of laughter and the clash of blade against blade. You cannot help but smile.

Message.SourceString: Well this didn't work out for me, did it? I made this great stupid journey, leaving Al Kharid behind, because adventure awaited me. Glory and fame.
Message.LocalizedString: Well this didn't work out for me, did it? I made this great stupid journey, leaving Al Kharid behind, because adventure awaited me. Glory and fame.

Message.SourceString: OoooOOooOOoooOOooo
Message.LocalizedString: OoooOOooOOoooOOooo

Message.SourceString: I never liked goblins, even though Zanik said they deserved our pity, more than hate.
Message.LocalizedString: I never liked goblins, even though Zanik said they deserved our pity, more than hate.

Message.SourceString: OoooOOooOOoooOOooo
Message.LocalizedString: OoooOOooOOoooOOooo

Message.SourceString: This shrine is a place where the dead are remembered. So that they may move on to the afterlife they deserve.
Message.LocalizedString: This shrine is a place where the dead are remembered. So that they may move on to the afterlife they deserve.

Message.SourceString: You do not have the space to receive your reward. You will need to make room in your backpack.
Message.LocalizedString: You do not have the space to receive your reward. You will need to make room in your backpack.

Message.SourceString: Thank you.
Message.LocalizedString: Thank you.

Message.LocalizedString: Thank you.

Message.SourceString: Thank you.
Message.LocalizedString: Thank you.

Message.SourceString: The lost, the dead and the once forgotten, are finally laid to rest. A gentle peace washes over you and you are left with a gift from the dead.
Message.LocalizedString: The lost, the dead and the once forgotten, are finally laid to rest. A gentle peace washes over you and you are left with a gift from the dead.

Message.SourceString: You smell sausages, bacon and the sizzling of eggs on the pan. Your stomach rumbles in response.
Message.LocalizedString: You smell sausages, bacon and the sizzling of eggs on the pan. Your stomach rumbles in response.

Message.LocalizedString: Choking on swamp gas. Ruined timber, mouldy and splintered. Sinking moment by moment into bitter, bleak, mud. Find the name of the buried, set them free.

Message.SourceString: You hear the sound of children playing and a woman laughing with them.
Message.LocalizedString: You hear the sound of children playing and a woman laughing with them.

Message.LocalizedString: This shrine is a place where the dead are remembered. So that they may move on to the afterlife they deserve.

Message.SourceString: Hurtling through the air, knowing everything was over. All I could think about was how I'd missed breakfast. Most important meal of the day, and I forgot it on my last one.
Message.LocalizedString: Hurtling through the air, knowing everything was over. All I could think about was how I'd missed breakfast. Most important meal of the day, and I forgot it on my last one.

Message.SourceString: Names Kay, adventurer. Remember me, won't you? Give me a proper goodbye.
Message.LocalizedString: Names Kay, adventurer. Remember me, won't you? Give me a proper goodbye.
